BEGIN_PGML

Estimate the sum of each expression, and choose an appropriate answer.

a. [`[$shift0]\,\frac{[$nums[$scramble{0}][0]]}{[$dens[$scramble{0}][0]]}-[$shift1]\,\frac{[$nums[$scramble{0}][1]]}{[$dens[$scramble{0}][1]]}`] is close to [__]{$popups[$scramble{0}]}

a. [`[$shift0]\,\frac{[$nums[$scramble{1}][0]]}{[$dens[$scramble{1}][0]]}-[$shift1]\,\frac{[$nums[$scramble{1}][1]]}{[$dens[$scramble{1}][1]]}`] is close to [__]{$popups[$scramble{1}]}

a. [`[$shift0]\,\frac{[$nums[$scramble{2}][0]]}{[$dens[$scramble{2}][0]]}-[$shift1]\,\frac{[$nums[$scramble{2}][1]]}{[$dens[$scramble{2}][1]]}`] is close to [__]{$popups[$scramble{2}]}

a. [`[$shift0]\,\frac{[$nums[$scramble{3}][0]]}{[$dens[$scramble{3}][0]]}-[$shift1]\,\frac{[$nums[$scramble{3}][1]]}{[$dens[$scramble{3}][1]]}`] is close to [__]{$popups[$scramble{3}]}

